				<h4>Highlights</h4>
				<ul class="highlights">
					<li class="bullet">I implemented the Financial Managment System for over 40 Hilton World Wide Hotels (Infor FMS SunSystems) as Primary Consultant, preparing project plan &amp; managing each on-site project by myself as the sole and senior consultant.</li>
					<li class="bullet">I successfully delivered Implementations and End User Training sessions in over 12 countries around the world.</li>
					<li class="bullet">I developed and implemented a HTE (OTA dialect) interface (C# .NET) for Hilton Japan. The solution is live in all Hilton properties within the region since 2008.</li>
					<li class="bullet">I provided the technical design as well as implemented this design with custom add-ons to the Financial Management System to provide complex business rules, reporting and segregation for the Hilton Turkey cluster platform. As well as lead the migration to the hosted cluster environment on-site (first IBM cloud, followed by migrating from IBM to Dell)</li>
					<li class="bullet">I enjoy to automate mine and other consultants&#x27; jobs as well as end-user workflow by providing intuitive solutions in scripting languages such as PowerShell, Python and Bash as well as develop Line of Business applications using Visual Studio Tools for Office and VBA.</li>
