					<p>Ludiino is a start-up in Vietnam focused on providing online booking, dashboards and scoreboard solutions to sports, starting with Golf in Vietnam.</p>
				</div>
				<h4>Highlights</h4>
				<ul class="highlights">
					<li class="bullet">Designed the Docker-based developer workflow using in-house hosted Gitlab. Studied and advised on suitable git-branching models and issue closing workflow for the developers. Some experience with Agile project management.</li>
					<li class="bullet">I was in charge of writing the Dockerfile and Docker-Compose setup to orchestrate the full stack (Nginx, uWSGI, Postgres), as well as prove the stack with a PoC AngularJS / Django REST Framework application before the development teams had implemented the actual application and hand over everything to the developers. I ensured a successful immutable infrastructure for staging, test and production environments in the cloud.</li>
					<li class="bullet">Designed and provided PoC for the AWS - S3 based upload forms and ensured proper IAM roles were created and used only by the API servers to issue signed policy documents. Ensured no secrets were committed to source control and all secrets were made available through environment variables when bringing up each environment.</li>
					<li class="bullet">Designed the real time messaging architecture to be added on top of the REST APIs, based on Redis and NodeJS.</li>
					<li class="bullet">Created a low-cost, single server git-receive, build and deploy server as a stop gap until proper Jenkins implementation was completed.</li>
					<li class="bullet">Troubleshoot and maintain Ubuntu and CoreOS servers in production.</li>
